property_details.description: Your search for the unsurpassed home will now to an end at Ajmera I Land Zeon. Pleasantly developed by Ajmera Realty and Infra India this project encompasses 240 units in a high-rise and well-planned tower. Further, Ajmera I Land Zeon Wadala price lie within the range of Rs. 2.75 Cr - 5.0 Cr.

address.area_details: Located close to the Lalbaugh Flyover, Wadala East is a low-density location in the Mumbai Harbor. It neighbors, some of the most promising residential locales in the city. With the availability of all the essential civic utilities, Wadala is a place to watch out for in the future.
